{"tid":728852,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"發現男友叫雞","createTime":"2018-07-04T05:29:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-04T09:19:12.000Z","uid":193366,"like":7,"dislike":77,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e0415a5d7186e2f43434f2fd7b26a02c01842bfa","tid":728852,"uid":193366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T05:29:47.000Z","msg":"同男朋友係long d<br />\n我香港佢台灣<br />\n最近有去台灣搵佢<br />\n佢就不嬲都比我用佢電話 <br />\n有次佢去沖涼 睇佢電話<br />\n無意中發現佢叫雞 點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我明可能男仔都有個方面既需求 但心中總係有條刺咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n扮冇野<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2e448bde68be09c4eba3b206cd760eeec7c4fec","tid":728852,"uid":2267,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T05:31:16.000Z","msg":"We do chicken right"},{"pid":"416b0ceca0c86976fce90254952f2efb20bd9256","tid":728852,"uid":177089,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T05:32:15.000Z","msg":"點解唔俾先 你又滿足唔到佢"},{"pid":"44d1419ed294422d4809014103715de812034363","tid":728852,"uid":171555,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T05:33:58.000Z","msg":"叫雞好過搵SP啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">不過台灣好興約炮</span></span>"},{"pid":"ff5641137ca2b593b9454b5c2c3c4e3492940b82","tid":728852,"uid":13160,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T05:36:15.000Z","msg":"你叫番鴨，一人一次？"},{"pid":"e5e39efa1236792f28693c021cd66727be46a33f","tid":728852,"uid":174601,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T05:36:56.000Z","msg":"講出黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n心有刺好過扮好人"},{"pid":"9d05301e7af381663e85f9806436025beb917019","tid":728852,"uid":176304,"like":3,"dislik